{"tid":395505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大突破！南極冰山下洞穴發現未知物種","createTime":"2017-09-11T00:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T09:23:44.000Z","uid":53947,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4259ed731c4fc119f0331014bdeb3fc351592fa0","tid":395505,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"新頭殼newtalk |&nbsp;林序家&nbsp;綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n發布 2017.09.09 | 00:37<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據一項研究，南極洲冰河下的溫暖洞穴可能存在一個秘密的動植物世界，包括未知物種在內，這些洞穴是因活火山散發出的蒸氣而形成，從洞穴回收的土壤樣本，已經從苔蘚，藻類和小動物中發現了有趣的DNA痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這項由澳洲國立大學（Australian National University）研究人員主導的研究，對南極羅斯島（Ross Island）伊里布斯活火山（Mount Erebus）周遭進行探索，顯示存在龐大的洞穴系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）8日報導，研究人員指出，這些洞穴是因活火山散發出的蒸氣而形成，溫度可能達攝氏25度，使冰凍表層底下存在整個動植物生態系的可能性增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n領導團隊的研究人員佛瑞塞（Ceridwen Fraser）表示，洞穴附近透著光，裡面很溫暖，穿件Ｔ恤就很舒適。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他說，對洞穴泥土取樣進行分析，結果發現了有趣跡象，即海藻、苔蘚和小動物的DNA，雖然這些DNA多半與在南極其他地區發現的海藻、苔蘚和無脊椎動物類似，但並非所有序列都能完整揭密。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佛瑞塞表示，研究結果讓人想一瞥南極冰層下方可能有何種生物，那裡甚至可能存在新品種動植物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緬因大學教授康奈爾（Laurie Connell）則表示，目前並未證實動植物仍然生活在洞穴中，「下一步將是仔細觀察洞穴，尋找活生物體，如果存在，就會打開一個人興奮的新世界的大門。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-09-09/97296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2017-09-09%2F97296&d=5ay%2F%2FW2H93mD75sgs%2Fvw08KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f1c9dfb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-09-09/97296</a>"},{"pid":"07f7619e14104c66f9137c43c20665b4ac5f97bd","tid":395505,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:05:46.000Z","msg":"諗起異獸戰1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb21017bf919c52cf4b12e13b2c66d76dd7363a","tid":395505,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:11:21.000Z","msg":"甚至可能有新物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701f2bd1e0fad80bd9949b40b7fde7e7f212694d","tid":395505,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲新物種係咪叫連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24cf5af322876fc351ecd77e520d61583856de84","tid":395505,"uid":49247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"The thing"},{"pid":"4363223807586e66bfc15268eb7d89418c94e3c5","tid":395505,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"唔少海底火山都有d幾得意既生態圈"},{"pid":"8eb34b4ef9a88c87d3d9a7abcdb23f5e55848577","tid":395505,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"megatron<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50793036e6a1e0380a312f598731df811179e6b","tid":395505,"uid":6590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"Eva <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6609e4ec9340f18603720d2b2f5300fbeacacbb","tid":395505,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"地底人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal